abstract: Google’s co-founder, Larry Page, is said to have bought himself a $45 million yacht that isn’t lacking for luxuries.

lead_paragraph: Facebook‘s Mark Zuckerberg may be the man of the moment, what with the Time Person of the Year award, the most hotly awaited impending initial public offering and a critically acclaimed movie loosely based on his life.

headline.main: Google Co-Founder Sets Sail on $45 Million Yacht
